davis-wx (0.1.0~alpha2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix chart y-axis scaling (areaspline threshold, summary-based bounds).
  * Add min/max summary and per-bucket extremes to history API.
  * Auto-scale temperature gauge range from current value and daily hi/lo.
  * Fix barometer calibration signed int16 handling.
  * Fix WeatherLink config crash when daemon not connected.
  * Cache hardware config to eliminate serial contention on config reads.
  * Add diagnostic logging for calibration reads.

